WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:13.320
{\an8}I'd like to announce something.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:20.959
{\an8}Thariq Ridzuwan and Husniya Radwa's matrimony will be canceled.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.680
{\an8}No! Mom!

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.679
{\an8}Correction.

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:34.680
{\an8}Our matrimony is not canceled, just postponed.

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:40.440
{\an8}Sir, could you give us one more hour?

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:45.960
{\an8}- All right. Just one hour. - Thank you.

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.920
You, stay out of this!

00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:54.320
This is my future husband's spot.

00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:59.960
No one deserves to sit here other than Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:01:02.960 --> 00:01:06.079
What else? Can't you see?

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:08.280
Your future husband isn't coming.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:11.560
Mom, I'm only asking for one hour.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:14.480
If he's still not here,

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:20.840
I agree to marry Zafir.

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.280
{\an8}Sit down, Husniya.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:49.279
Aiman said the Holy Dragon team hasn't returned from the operation.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.280
- All of them? - All of them.

00:01:55.560 --> 00:02:01.239
Husniya, breathe.

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:03.239
It's okay.

00:02:03.240 --> 00:02:09.000
Dahlia, I cannot marry Zafir. I don't want to.

00:02:09.720 --> 00:02:11.159
We can run. There's still time.

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:15.000
I cannot. I have to wait for Ridz. I know he'll come.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:17.440
He won't do this to me.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.520
Unless something has happened to him.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.960
Dahlia, I'm scared.

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:31.000
Radwa, are you okay?

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:33.840
Mom.

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:39.160
I'm scared. What if something has happened to Ridz?

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:55.520
Ridz, I don't understand why you've been sleeping for so long.

00:02:57.080 --> 00:03:00.360
You're not that badly injured. Why are you not waking up?

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:03.800
You're supposed to be marrying Radwa this morning.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.240
And now you're awake.

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:12.520
Do you not understand what I'm saying?

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:15.120
Treasure.

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:39.680
Where are you going, sir?

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:43.880
Bye!

00:03:49.720 --> 00:03:55.200
I'm sure Ridz is trying his best to come home right now.

00:03:58.720 --> 00:03:59.880
Time's up!

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.239
You asked for one hour. I gave you one hour.

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:06.119
The officiant is leaving. Take her.

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:10.400
Mom, wait. Let's wait a little longer. I feel that Ridz will be here.

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:15.879
I'm not waiting anymore. I gave you one hour!

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:19.000
Where is he? Where is that guy who's saving you?

00:04:21.279 --> 00:04:24.919
- Enough. Take her! - Calm down.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.480
Please give some more time.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:28.840
Don't you pity Radwa?

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:33.439
If you want help, don't ask me.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:35.200
Go and ask the police for help!

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:40.080
Mom, please. I don't want to!

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:44.960
Sit down!

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:50.719
Sir, you may start. The bride is here.

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.799
All right. Let's start.

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:55.560
In the name of God.

00:04:56.600 --> 00:05:00.879
- Thariq Ridzuwan bin... - Auntie, let it go!

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:01.920
Yes.

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:05.199
I'm marrying you

00:05:05.200 --> 00:05:08.199
to Husniya Radwa binti Husaini,

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:11.639
represented by me with RM8,000 worth of dowry,

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:14.640
and a golden bracelet.

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:17.799
I accept to be wedded to Husniya Radwa binti Husaini

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:21.160
with RM8,000 worth of dowry, and a golden bracelet.

00:05:34.280 --> 00:05:36.039
You're an ungrateful daughter.

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:42.720
Listen. I will always pray that you will never be happy!

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:45.760
Oh God. Mom!

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.160
Treasure?

00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:01.200
What's the matter?

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:22.560
I love you so much, my wife.

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:30.960
There's blood.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:33.360
I'm okay.

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:38.080
- I'm okay. - Walk!

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.039
Listen.

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:47.920
Next time, you can try to ruin another wedding.

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:01.040
- Bear with it. - I am.

00:07:02.600 --> 00:07:04.760
The person who did this to you is cruel.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:06.880
Wait.

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:09.480
What did you say?

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:14.919
- The person who did this to-- - You were nice to me.

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:17.160
Instead of being rude, you're being polite.

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:22.759
But yes, the person is really bad.

00:07:22.760 --> 00:07:26.560
When you see him, could you scold him for me?

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:29.360
Then do this.

00:07:32.880 --> 00:07:36.679
- Do I know this person? - Of course. It's me.

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:38.400
I did it myself.

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.880
Don't play around!

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:46.200
I'm your husband.

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:48.440
Okay?

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.320
No sorry?

00:07:53.880 --> 00:07:55.840
Fine. I'm sorry.

00:07:58.200 --> 00:08:01.320
But seriously. I'm not playing around.

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:03.880
I am being serious.

00:08:08.600 --> 00:08:10.719
I wanted to come home as soon as I could.

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:15.079
I wanted to make sure that I didn't break my promise

00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:17.519
to marry you today.

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:20.479
Even though I was an hour late, I'm sorry.

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:22.799
Did you know that I almost married someone else?

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.640
I know. I'm sorry.

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:32.120
Husniya,

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:35.480
as long as I'm alive,

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:39.760
I will never neglect you.

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:44.640
I promise.

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:34.600
I promise that you will be the happiest wife in the world.

00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:39.640
I promise.

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:06.520
How could you guys not invite us?

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:14.000
Not the ceremony, not even the reception.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.239
You're treating me like a stranger

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:19.240
when we're siblings.

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:25.600
Now that you have a daughter-in-law, you don't love me anymore.

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:28.120
Do you really think so?

00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:32.279
I always think of you.

00:11:32.280 --> 00:11:35.400
I love you so much.

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:37.920
If I did not,

00:11:39.640 --> 00:11:42.119
I would have sent you to prison a long time ago.

00:11:42.120 --> 00:11:45.000
Why would you send me to prison?

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:48.600
Did you think I didn't know?

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:54.280
Who ruined Radwa's clothes? It was you, wasn't it?

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:58.080
Enough. Stop accusing.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:03.200
If you don't have any proof, it will be slander.

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:07.400
I thought we could be in-laws. But things turned out this way.

00:12:08.280 --> 00:12:11.799
Oh God. What do you mean?

00:12:11.800 --> 00:12:16.240
We share the same parents. We're siblings.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.920
Isn't that enough?

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:23.759
- Peace be upon you. - And peace be upon you.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:26.679
You're home. Come in, Radwa.

00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:29.560
Her dress is very heavy.

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:38.520
Auntie, this is my wife, Radwa. The one you've been asking about.

00:12:39.320 --> 00:12:40.599
Auntie.

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:42.440
Do you think she meets all the criteria?

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:47.640
Okay, we're going upstairs. But I have something to say.

00:12:48.880 --> 00:12:53.240
Dad was outstation before this. And now, he's here.

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:56.479
If possible, don't stay here too long.

00:12:56.480 --> 00:13:02.400
We don't want another version of a cheating scandal here.

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:07.840
Ridz, stop it.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:10.759
Okay, we'll go upstairs. We're tired.

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:12.640
Auntie, sorry.

00:13:16.520 --> 00:13:18.320
Why would you wear that dress?

00:13:20.920 --> 00:13:22.240
Are you okay?

00:13:32.400 --> 00:13:34.760
- Can you walk? - Not really.

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:49.760
My wife is really beautiful.

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:52.240
Thank you.

00:13:55.720 --> 00:13:56.880
Can I ask you something?

00:13:58.440 --> 00:14:01.119
Why didn't Thalia come to our wedding?

00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:02.599
Thalia?

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:05.799
She's working in the US. She'll be here next week.

00:14:05.800 --> 00:14:07.560
We'll see her then. Okay?

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:14.560
Can I ask you something?

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:19.160
Do you love me, your dearest husband?

00:14:21.040 --> 00:14:22.320
Seriously?

00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:25.479
I will not call you that.

00:14:25.480 --> 00:14:27.920
Okay. Well...

00:14:29.280 --> 00:14:32.159
if you don't want that,

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.680
call me

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:36.760
stinky.

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:40.200
Sure.

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:45.640
You really are extremely stinky. Right?

00:14:56.160 --> 00:14:59.000
Darling, are you okay?

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:02.480
No, let me do it.

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:09.399
Is it a trend nowadays

00:15:09.400 --> 00:15:13.760
to wear a hijab that takes three days to remove?

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:18.840
I love you so much.

00:15:19.520 --> 00:15:22.360
I hate you.

00:15:32.040 --> 00:15:36.680
Why didn't you come to save me?

00:15:50.520 --> 00:15:53.000
Miss, let's eat.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:59.759
Don't do this. You must eat.

00:15:59.760 --> 00:16:04.440
The boss wants you to be happy, healthy, and well-fed.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:09.720
I have been kidnapped.

00:16:10.640 --> 00:16:13.279
How could I possibly feel happy or healthy?

00:16:13.280 --> 00:16:15.280
Do you think this is a holiday?

00:16:17.680 --> 00:16:19.919
Miss, don't do this.

00:16:19.920 --> 00:16:22.360
I don't want to end up like Ms. Wan.

00:16:26.080 --> 00:16:27.360
What happened to her?

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:33.159
She's gone. She's been killed.

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:34.720
She's dead.

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:40.760
Okay. I'll eat it now.

00:16:41.760 --> 00:16:43.640
Let me feed you.

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:52.160
Darling.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:57.799
Darling, what's the matter?

00:16:57.800 --> 00:16:59.680
What's the matter?

00:17:04.119 --> 00:17:06.640
Are you okay? It's me.

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:09.440
What were you dreaming about?

00:17:10.599 --> 00:17:15.599
I'm here with you. Calm down.

00:17:16.599 --> 00:17:19.040
I seek forgiveness from God, the Great.

00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:22.000
I seek forgiveness from God, the Great.

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.680
I seek forgiveness from God, the Great.

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.280
Let me get you some water.

00:17:34.360 --> 00:17:39.480
But you weren't there when I really needed you.

00:17:47.760 --> 00:17:48.960
Dear God,

00:17:50.280 --> 00:17:54.000
protect my family from the evil of humans and devils.

00:17:55.200 --> 00:18:00.320
Bless our marriage with Your love and grace.

00:18:01.920 --> 00:18:03.680
Amen.

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:15.000
Darling, can I ask you something?

00:18:18.280 --> 00:18:19.920
Last night, you had a nightmare.

00:18:23.080 --> 00:18:24.240
What was the dream about?

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:34.000
Good morning, Ridz!

00:18:36.920 --> 00:18:40.560
Come for breakfast. Your mom made fried rice.

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:45.959
How many times have I told you not to come into my room?

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:48.839
- I'm sorry. - What are you doing?

00:18:48.840 --> 00:18:53.160
Oh, honey. Look at our daughter.

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:58.160
Usually, only children do this kind of thing.

00:18:58.760 --> 00:19:02.119
If you're a mature adult, you wouldn't do something like this.

00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:04.479
You're right. Only immature adults.

00:19:04.480 --> 00:19:06.440
Go downstairs!

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:10.840
Stop making that face. You'll haunt this room.

00:19:11.360 --> 00:19:12.880
Go and take a shower!

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:21.480
Why is she messing around so early in the morning?

00:19:28.560 --> 00:19:30.040
Did you wake Ridz up?

00:19:31.160 --> 00:19:33.040
Why would she?

00:19:33.560 --> 00:19:35.320
He already has a wife.

00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:38.360
His wife can wake him.

00:19:39.920 --> 00:19:42.320
I don't think Radwa is awake yet.

00:19:44.840 --> 00:19:47.719
What about the morning prayer? Did they skip it?

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:49.279
Right?

00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:53.000
I would be embarrassed to wake up late if I were her.

00:19:54.760 --> 00:19:55.640
Really?

00:19:57.080 --> 00:20:02.000
But I notice that you wake up late when you're here too.

00:20:04.200 --> 00:20:07.239
- Morning, Mom. - Morning, darling.

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:09.320
- Where's Radwa? - She's upstairs.

00:20:09.920 --> 00:20:12.960
She's so lucky to be Ridz's wife.

00:20:14.320 --> 00:20:16.680
She'll have food served right in front of her.

00:20:18.040 --> 00:20:19.800
She's not feeling well.

00:20:20.840 --> 00:20:23.720
- Morning, Mom. - Morning, dear.

00:20:25.920 --> 00:20:27.720
Auntie, Aina.

00:20:28.320 --> 00:20:30.560
I thought you were unwell. Why did you come down?

00:20:31.480 --> 00:20:33.279
It was nothing serious.

00:20:33.280 --> 00:20:37.639
Once I stay close to Ridz, I feel better already.

00:20:37.640 --> 00:20:42.120
Don't be so spoiled. Go back upstairs.

00:20:42.840 --> 00:20:47.680
You might spread it to us. Let Ridz stay here.

00:20:48.360 --> 00:20:50.359
I can't do that.

00:20:50.360 --> 00:20:53.840
He'll lose his appetite looking at your face.

00:20:54.440 --> 00:20:55.880
He'll probably feel nauseous.

00:20:57.040 --> 00:21:00.400
I have to be here so he keeps his appetite.

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:04.720
How did you find her?

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.039
She's rude.

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:09.440
Really rude.

00:21:10.360 --> 00:21:11.960
I've lost my appetite.

00:21:28.800 --> 00:21:31.200
Dear, what are you doing?

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:35.439
I'll wipe the dishes, and you can wipe the counter.

00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:36.520
I'm helping you.

00:21:38.480 --> 00:21:40.480
Won't your mom get upset if you do this?

00:21:42.640 --> 00:21:44.440
Why would she?

00:21:45.600 --> 00:21:47.239
She would be proud of me

00:21:47.240 --> 00:21:49.400
for being a good husband to you.

00:21:50.240 --> 00:21:51.159
Right?

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:52.800
Exactly.

00:21:57.280 --> 00:21:59.520
Darling, there.

00:22:00.280 --> 00:22:01.800
Who's calling?

00:22:03.760 --> 00:22:04.720
Adrean.

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:08.560
Hello.

00:22:11.320 --> 00:22:13.120
Okay. No problem.

00:22:20.680 --> 00:22:22.320
Work?

00:22:25.320 --> 00:22:26.640
Work.

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:33.080
Go. It's okay.

00:22:34.240 --> 00:22:36.479
Don't worry about me.

00:22:36.480 --> 00:22:39.960
Darling, I'm sorry. I already applied for leave, but...

00:22:41.640 --> 00:22:44.520
Our battlefields are different.

00:22:46.800 --> 00:22:47.840
Isn't that a song?

00:22:49.960 --> 00:22:51.640
- Really? - Yeah.

00:22:52.840 --> 00:22:54.920
Can you try singing it?

00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:09.240
I'm sorry.

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:12.280
Take care.

00:23:13.800 --> 00:23:15.080
Okay.

00:23:24.160 --> 00:23:26.720
Stop pretending like you know nothing.

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:31.360
Just by looking at your face, I already know.

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:35.680
Westerners say,

00:23:36.680 --> 00:23:38.880
"Don't judge a book by its cover."

00:23:41.280 --> 00:23:42.600
Understood?

00:23:44.520 --> 00:23:46.720
I'm done fighting you guys.

00:23:47.680 --> 00:23:50.080
You guys aren't that bad.

00:23:51.160 --> 00:23:55.600
If you don't have a job later, you can come work for me.

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:02.719
- Who's your boss? - Go to hell.

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:04.880
Don't waste our time.

00:24:05.480 --> 00:24:07.000
Make it quick.

00:24:07.720 --> 00:24:09.480
Before I lose my temper.

00:24:10.920 --> 00:24:12.760
You only think about yourself.

00:24:13.280 --> 00:24:15.320
What about mine?

00:24:17.920 --> 00:24:21.480
I told you. I know nothing.

00:24:23.480 --> 00:24:24.800
You look...

00:24:26.120 --> 00:24:27.400
like you will be dead soon.

00:24:28.800 --> 00:24:32.040
You should start looking for a burial service.

00:24:33.320 --> 00:24:34.960
What a joke.

00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:36.640
Do you think I'm scared?

00:24:39.560 --> 00:24:41.760
Even if I tell you,

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:45.359
we will both die.

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:46.760
Exactly.

00:24:48.040 --> 00:24:51.600
Listen, tell me who your boss is.

00:24:52.360 --> 00:24:54.040
I'll promise you one thing.

00:24:55.720 --> 00:24:58.680
I'll protect you and your family.

00:25:00.760 --> 00:25:02.800
If you agree,

00:25:03.560 --> 00:25:05.480
then sign here.

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:08.920
How?

00:25:09.800 --> 00:25:11.280
Will you sign?

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:14.239
It's fine if you don't.

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:16.280
You're threatening me?

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:20.320
Do you know who I am?

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:22.520
Listen.

00:25:23.320 --> 00:25:25.839
A tiger cannot change its stripes

00:25:25.840 --> 00:25:30.160
and cannot be tamed.

00:25:35.480 --> 00:25:37.480
Relax. Don't get too serious.

00:25:38.080 --> 00:25:39.440
People might hate you.

00:25:41.640 --> 00:25:44.440
Wait, let me think.

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:48.719
His name starts with...

00:25:48.720 --> 00:25:49.799
the letter C.

00:25:49.800 --> 00:25:51.720
Hold on.

00:25:54.440 --> 00:25:56.120
Now I remember.

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:59.960
His name starts with...

00:26:01.600 --> 00:26:03.240
the letter Z.

00:26:15.920 --> 00:26:16.880
Thank you, Dato' Syed.

00:26:17.480 --> 00:26:22.800
May our business bring more income and opportunities.

00:26:23.800 --> 00:26:25.320
God willing.

00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:38.640
Aina!

00:26:41.760 --> 00:26:43.559
How did you enter this room?

00:26:43.560 --> 00:26:46.600
The door was open, so I came in.

00:26:47.840 --> 00:26:50.520
You're lying. I locked the door.

00:26:52.320 --> 00:26:54.639
You're right. It was locked.

00:26:54.640 --> 00:26:59.879
But Ridz gave me a spare key to this room.

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:04.960
So I can come in here anytime.

00:27:05.960 --> 00:27:09.279
From now on, you can't enter this room as you please.

00:27:09.280 --> 00:27:11.839
- What do you mean? - It's not your room!

00:27:11.840 --> 00:27:14.439
This is Ridz's and my bedroom!

00:27:14.440 --> 00:27:15.760
Hey.

00:27:17.520 --> 00:27:19.160
What is all this commotion?

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:22.520
It's Radwa.

00:27:23.120 --> 00:27:25.680
She won't let me enter this room.

00:27:29.240 --> 00:27:31.920
For your information,

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:35.480
they grew up together.

00:27:36.840 --> 00:27:40.440
So Aina doesn't need anyone's permission to be in this room.

00:27:41.280 --> 00:27:44.520
You've only been here one day and already acting like this?

00:27:45.760 --> 00:27:50.119
Growing up together doesn't give you the right to act like this!

00:27:50.120 --> 00:27:52.719
It has only been a day, but I still have my rights.

00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:54.799
I am still Ridz's wife!

00:27:54.800 --> 00:27:58.280
You can't just open these gifts. It's a sin.

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:06.200
You act like God, talking about sin.

00:28:07.520 --> 00:28:10.880
Ridz is so unlucky to have a wife like you.

00:28:12.560 --> 00:28:14.159
That's it, Aina. Let's go.

00:28:14.160 --> 00:28:16.520
We're not desperate for cheap gifts like this.

00:28:17.200 --> 00:28:19.200
Wait, Auntie.

00:28:20.440 --> 00:28:21.880
I'm sorry.

00:28:22.480 --> 00:28:26.479
Aina does have the right to enter any room in this house

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:28.120
because she's the maid.

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:31.520
Watch your mouth.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:10.480
<i>Ridz is so unlucky to have a wife like you.</i>

00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:19.120
Was I wrong for marrying Ridz?

00:29:22.080 --> 00:29:23.280
Darling.

00:29:24.360 --> 00:29:25.520
Dear.

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:29.640
Why are you sitting here? Are you not feeling well?

00:29:31.080 --> 00:29:32.560
I'm fine.

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:38.720
I was in our room and saw that our presents had been opened.

00:29:39.680 --> 00:29:43.560
Why didn't you wait for me? Should I be sulking?

00:29:45.400 --> 00:29:48.160
It was not me. It was Aina.

00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:51.399
She came into our room and opened everything.

00:29:51.400 --> 00:29:53.640
Oh, dear. Darling, I'm sorry.

00:29:59.080 --> 00:29:59.960
Dear,

00:30:01.840 --> 00:30:03.520
am I a bad person?

00:30:04.840 --> 00:30:07.159
At home, Mom hates me.

00:30:07.160 --> 00:30:10.479
Here, Auntie and Aina hate me.

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:11.960
Darling.

00:30:12.800 --> 00:30:14.600
You're not. Not at all.

00:30:16.920 --> 00:30:22.000
But everyone wants me to suffer and wants our marriage to fail.

00:30:22.960 --> 00:30:25.640
I'm afraid that they'll get what they want.

00:30:31.560 --> 00:30:33.280
Darling.

00:30:34.240 --> 00:30:35.800
There was once

00:30:37.040 --> 00:30:39.000
a companion of the Prophet.

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:42.440
Sa'ad Ibn Abi Waqqas.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:45.880
He was often slandered.

00:30:47.080 --> 00:30:50.600
One day, he prayed to Allah.

00:30:51.360 --> 00:30:54.080
And Allah granted his prayer. Do you know why?

00:30:54.920 --> 00:30:58.920
Because the prayer of the oppressed has no barrier before Allah.

00:31:01.560 --> 00:31:03.920
So pray for good things.

00:31:04.520 --> 00:31:06.320
Believe in good things.

00:31:07.080 --> 00:31:08.600
Good things will come to you.

00:31:09.200 --> 00:31:10.080
Okay?

00:31:12.280 --> 00:31:17.280
Okay, listen, let's go for a staycation tomorrow.

00:31:18.040 --> 00:31:21.319
A honeymoon. Let's forget all this.

00:31:21.320 --> 00:31:22.440
Do you want to?

00:31:24.440 --> 00:31:25.600
Okay.

00:31:26.760 --> 00:31:29.880
Don't think too much.

00:31:40.440 --> 00:31:41.840
I want to come with you.

00:31:42.760 --> 00:31:44.720
That's right. You should take her.

00:31:45.880 --> 00:31:49.599
Why should I? No one takes a maid on their honeymoon.

00:31:49.600 --> 00:31:52.160
Ridz, that's not nice.

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:54.240
What do you mean?

00:31:55.920 --> 00:31:58.039
Then what about you coming into my room

00:31:58.040 --> 00:31:59.959
and destroying all my things?

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:01.360
Is it nice?

00:32:03.080 --> 00:32:06.120
Auntie, did you not teach her manners?

00:32:07.840 --> 00:32:10.799
She's an adult. She's not a kid anymore. She should know better.

00:32:10.800 --> 00:32:11.919
Give me back the keys.

00:32:11.920 --> 00:32:13.239
Ridz,

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:15.999
I did not expect you to believe

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:19.319
a stranger over your family.

00:32:19.320 --> 00:32:20.560
Who's the stranger?

00:32:21.240 --> 00:32:22.240
Her?

00:32:23.040 --> 00:32:24.280
She's my wife.

00:32:25.920 --> 00:32:27.800
Stop acting.

00:32:29.360 --> 00:32:30.520
This house has CCTV cameras.

00:32:32.360 --> 00:32:34.119
Auntie,

00:32:34.120 --> 00:32:36.000
I'm terribly sorry.

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:41.240
It seems my respect for you is fading.

00:32:41.880 --> 00:32:45.040
If you and Aina mess with Radwa again,

00:32:46.400 --> 00:32:50.880
that will be the last time you and Aina stay in this house.

00:32:54.440 --> 00:32:55.680
Darling, let's go.

00:33:10.120 --> 00:33:11.880
Peace be upon you.

00:33:13.320 --> 00:33:14.480
Ta-da!

00:33:24.960 --> 00:33:27.480
Darling, hold on. Wait here.

00:33:42.760 --> 00:33:43.920
Ta-da!

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:48.000
For you. Here.

00:33:55.440 --> 00:33:56.800
Do you like it?

00:34:03.920 --> 00:34:05.880
Did you prepare all this?

00:34:09.840 --> 00:34:11.199
Thank you.

00:34:14.159 --> 00:34:15.600
Just "thank you"?

00:34:16.280 --> 00:34:17.520
No "I love you"?

00:34:18.719 --> 00:34:19.920
Of course.

00:34:21.400 --> 00:34:22.320
I...

00:34:23.560 --> 00:34:24.880
hate you.

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:38.400
Dear.

00:34:40.400 --> 00:34:42.000
Can I say something?

00:34:45.920 --> 00:34:48.198
You're making me worried.

00:34:48.199 --> 00:34:50.280
But what is it?

00:34:53.159 --> 00:34:55.559
I don't feel good

00:34:55.560 --> 00:34:59.040
seeing you fight with Aina and Auntie

00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:01.280
because of me.

00:35:02.920 --> 00:35:04.040
Why?

00:35:05.760 --> 00:35:07.160
Because they're my family?

00:35:12.960 --> 00:35:14.160
Darling.

00:35:15.600 --> 00:35:20.920
Whether they're family or not,

00:35:22.080 --> 00:35:25.360
if they hurt my treasure, I can't let it be.

00:35:27.440 --> 00:35:29.640
Families...

00:35:31.040 --> 00:35:32.800
shouldn't treat us that way.

00:35:33.720 --> 00:35:38.160
Those who treat us that way don't deserve to be in our lives.

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:43.040
Right?

00:35:44.520 --> 00:35:46.800
Darling, wait.

00:35:48.400 --> 00:35:50.000
Hold on, I...

00:35:51.480 --> 00:35:53.680
I heard something.

00:35:54.720 --> 00:35:56.440
I think it was telling me something.

00:35:59.760 --> 00:36:02.880
I really heard something. I did.

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:06.639
- It came from there. - Do it again.

00:36:06.640 --> 00:36:09.439
No, it came from there. I heard it.

00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:11.480
What sound was it?

00:36:14.320 --> 00:36:16.600
- Are you hungry? - I am.

00:36:17.440 --> 00:36:20.120
- Let's eat. - What did it sound like again?

00:36:26.480 --> 00:36:28.800
- Fried chicken. - No.

00:36:29.720 --> 00:36:31.479
Today,

00:36:31.480 --> 00:36:33.120
let me feed you.

00:36:34.320 --> 00:36:35.840
Okay.

00:36:38.920 --> 00:36:40.240
It's hot.

00:36:41.560 --> 00:36:43.039
- Is it good? - It is.

00:36:43.040 --> 00:36:44.559
One more.

00:36:44.560 --> 00:36:47.599
- Aren't you eating? - You first.

00:36:47.600 --> 00:36:49.240
I like watching you eat.

00:36:50.880 --> 00:36:52.000
One more.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:57.960
Darling, why?

00:36:58.760 --> 00:37:00.320
Nothing.

00:37:07.920 --> 00:37:09.320
One more.

00:37:11.600 --> 00:37:13.960
Darling, what's the matter?

00:37:15.480 --> 00:37:19.080
Dear, it feels like someone is watching us.

00:37:29.440 --> 00:37:31.639
Darling, if you're uncomfortable, let's go back to the hotel.

00:37:31.640 --> 00:37:33.240
Let's just eat in our room.

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:35.320
Okay.

00:37:36.840 --> 00:37:38.280
Wash your hands.

00:38:12.160 --> 00:38:13.440
You.

00:38:14.800 --> 00:38:16.240
What do you want?

00:38:30.200 --> 00:38:31.400
Radwa?

00:38:34.120 --> 00:38:35.680
Radwa and Ridz.

00:38:38.960 --> 00:38:40.640
Do you want me to break them up?

00:39:10.920 --> 00:39:13.799
<i>Hello, baby. Where are you?</i>

00:39:13.800 --> 00:39:14.920
I miss you.

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:03.960
Darling?

00:40:07.880 --> 00:40:09.280
You're going to bed already?

00:40:10.600 --> 00:40:13.439
<i>Hello, baby. Where are you?</i>

00:40:13.440 --> 00:40:15.279
<i>I miss you.</i>

00:40:15.280 --> 00:40:17.560
Why are you wearing your hijab to bed?

00:40:28.080 --> 00:40:29.520
Darling?

00:40:31.600 --> 00:40:32.760
Darling.

00:40:44.960 --> 00:40:45.880
Hey!

00:40:57.240 --> 00:40:59.799
Darling? Hey!

00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:04.959
What's the matter? Tell me. I'm here with you. Why are you scared?

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:07.559
I'm here with you. Why?

00:41:07.560 --> 00:41:09.360
You're a liar!

00:41:11.240 --> 00:41:13.919
Darling, what are you saying?

00:41:13.920 --> 00:41:17.560
You weren't with me. You were too busy with Anita.

00:41:18.200 --> 00:41:22.680
Five years! You left me just like that.

00:41:23.400 --> 00:41:28.400
I had to go through so much with Mom and my sisters.

00:41:29.240 --> 00:41:31.960
On campus, at the office.

00:41:33.560 --> 00:41:35.559
I was alone.

00:41:35.560 --> 00:41:36.960
Darling, hey...

00:41:38.520 --> 00:41:42.440
I was hurting.

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:45.440
But do you know what hurt the most?

00:41:50.680 --> 00:41:52.880
You weren't there

00:41:53.720 --> 00:41:56.720
when I really needed you.

00:42:01.600 --> 00:42:07.160
- I prayed day and night. - Darling...

00:42:07.960 --> 00:42:10.399
But you weren't there.

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:11.960
Treasure.

00:42:14.080 --> 00:42:17.120
I don't know how to tell you.

00:42:18.040 --> 00:42:20.640
I was there.

00:42:23.120 --> 00:42:25.760
I've always been there for you.

00:42:49.960 --> 00:42:51.560
It was you?

00:42:52.120 --> 00:42:54.120
You saved me?

00:42:59.960 --> 00:43:02.880
I never forgot you

00:43:03.480 --> 00:43:05.920
during those five years we were apart.

00:43:14.480 --> 00:43:16.200
Darling.

00:43:20.720 --> 00:43:22.200
Darling.

00:43:27.920 --> 00:43:29.360
All this time,

00:43:30.040 --> 00:43:31.799
I blamed you.

00:43:31.800 --> 00:43:34.920
I was really upset about our fate.

00:43:35.440 --> 00:43:38.359
- I accused you. - I'm sorry, okay?

00:43:38.360 --> 00:43:40.160
No.

00:43:41.680 --> 00:43:44.880
I'm sorry. I should be the one apologizing.

00:43:48.200 --> 00:43:49.520
Dear.

00:43:52.320 --> 00:43:54.319
I have one more thing to discuss.

00:43:54.320 --> 00:43:56.000
About Anita?

00:43:58.000 --> 00:43:59.520
I know.

00:44:01.760 --> 00:44:05.000
I swear there's nothing going on between us.

00:44:06.400 --> 00:44:08.520
I believe you.

00:44:11.080 --> 00:44:13.440
Believing you is my choice.

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:17.520
But it's your responsibility

00:44:18.560 --> 00:44:22.559
to make sure that believing you is not a mistake.

00:44:22.560 --> 00:44:24.880
I will not take it for granted.

00:44:27.880 --> 00:44:30.320
I'm only asking for one thing.

00:44:33.320 --> 00:44:35.120
Promise me.

00:44:39.040 --> 00:44:42.480
No matter how bad our arguments get,

00:44:44.440 --> 00:44:46.360
we must put aside our egos.

00:44:50.400 --> 00:44:53.280
What matters is that we try to be happy.

00:44:57.040 --> 00:44:58.280
Okay?

00:45:00.640 --> 00:45:03.320
Darling, I can't lose you.

00:45:07.560 --> 00:45:09.640
I love you so much.

00:45:16.800 --> 00:45:19.440
{\an8}And I love you too, Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:45:26.560 --> 00:45:30.880
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

00:45:38.760 --> 00:45:43.039
{\an8}<i>I don't want him to use Teduh as a front for his illegal activities.</i>

00:45:43.040 --> 00:45:46.199
{\an8}We'll name this merger Teduh Kasih Home

00:45:46.200 --> 00:45:49.399
{\an8}and I don't see anyone else capable of handling this place

00:45:49.400 --> 00:45:50.479
{\an8}other than you.

00:45:50.480 --> 00:45:54.199
{\an8}I don't understand how someone like you can escape unpunished.

00:45:54.200 --> 00:45:57.319
{\an8}I will never leave you in peace

00:45:57.320 --> 00:46:00.239
{\an8}until I get what's mine.

00:46:00.240 --> 00:46:02.519
{\an8}Get lost! Go!

00:46:02.520 --> 00:46:03.919
{\an8}<i>Shut up!</i>

00:46:03.920 --> 00:46:05.520
{\an8}<i>If you want to live.</i>

00:46:06.400 --> 00:46:07.759
{\an8}Where did you take her?

00:46:07.760 --> 00:46:08.920
{\an8}Answer me!

